text: The Carina-Sagittarius Arm is one of the minor spiral arm of the Milky Way Galaxy. The other ones are located also in the Milky Way. The Carina- Sagittarius Arm has a number of Messier objectd: * Messier 11 * Messier 26 * Messier 16 * Messier 17 * Messier 18 * Messier 55 * Messier 24 * Messier 21 * The Lagoon Nebula(M8) And contains one non Messier object *NGC 3372
